<para>
  When the <varname>solver_mode</varname> argument to <xref
  linkend="MenuItem-OOF.Subproblem.Set_Solver"/> is
  <classname>AdvancedSolverMode</classname>, &oof2; leaves all of the
  detailed decisions about the <link
  linkend="Section-Concepts-Mesh-Solvers">solution method</link> to
  the user.  The settings of the <link
  linkend="RegisteredClass-StepDriver"><varname>time_stepper</varname></link>,
  <link
  linkend="RegisteredClass-NonlinearSolverBase"><varname>nonlinear_solver</varname></link>,
  <link
  linkend="RegisteredClass-MatrixMethod"><varname>symmetric_solver</varname></link>,
  and <link
  linkend="RegisteredClass-MatrixMethod"><varname>asymmetric_solver</varname></link>
  determine how the &subproblem;'s equations will be solved.
</para>

